item.description:
The CATALOGUE System introduced by BeArt represents a patented technology focused on achieving a 100% genuine on-chain mapping of art RWA assets, akin to a &ldquo;minting system&rdquo; for artistic assets. The CATALOGUE System comprises two fundamental functionalities: &ldquo;Certification&rdquo; and &ldquo;Art Gene Card.&rdquo;
Certification: This involves a blockchain-based system combined with interdisciplinary science to provide identity authentication and authenticity verification for artworks.
Art Gene Card: This is the data credential and visual representation result of the CATALOGUE System, presenting a unique identification RWA asset gene card (archive).
